Introduction

Do HanSe is the main rapper and lead dancer of the boy group Victon under The Dial Music. Despite his cool and chic charms, Hanse is described as one of the sweetest members.

Hanse debuted as a member of VICTON on November 9, 2016, with the mini album, "Voice To New World."

Hanse released his first solo album, BLAZE, on September 25, 2021. On April 20, 2023, IST Entertainment announced his departure from the group following the expiration of his exclusive contract.

On August 11, 2023, Hanse signed with The Dial Music. His first digital single, "How Time Flies," was released on March 18, 2024.
